---
// Hero.astro - Corregido con elipses y cruz superior
---
<section class="relative bg-white py-12 lg:py-16 px-6 lg:px-20 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between min-h-[700px] lg:min-h-[600px] overflow-hidden">
  
  <img 
    src="/images/component1.png" 
    alt="" 
    class="absolute top-[5%] left-[5%] lg:top-[10%] lg:left-15 w-[8%] lg:w-[3%] max-w-[50px] z-20 opacity-90"
  />

  <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 space-y-6 lg:space-y-8 z-10 text-center lg:text-left mt-8 lg:mt-0">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-normal text-[#003366] leading-tight font-montserrat">
      Atención Médica Integral y <br class="hidden lg:block"/>
      <span class="text-[#0056b3] font-black">Ambulancias UCI 24/7</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-base lg:text-lg max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0 font-montserrat">
      Soporte avanzado y ambulancias UCI las 24 horas. Conexión inmediata entre El Vigía, San Cristóbal, Mérida y el Sur del Lago.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
      <a href="#" class="w-full sm:w-auto bg-[#0056b3] inline-flex items-center justify-center text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-800 transition-all shadow-lg font-montserrat">
        Llamar Emergencia
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="ml-3">
          <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
          <path d="M15 2h6v6"></path>
          <path d="M15 8l6-6"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="w-full sm:w-auto border-2 border-black text-black px-10 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-all font-montserrat flex items-center justify-center">
        Afíliate Ahora
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative w-full lg:w-1/2 mt-16 lg:mt-0 flex justify-center items-center">
    <img 
      src="/images/elipsi.png" 
      alt="" 
      class="absolute right-[-5%] lg:right-[-10%] top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[90%] lg:w-[100%] max-w-[600px] z-0 opacity-90"
    />
    
    <img 
      src="/images/hero.png" 
      alt="Personal Sima24" 
      class="relative z-10 w-[95%] lg:w-full max-w-[550px] drop-shadow-2xl" 
    />
    
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-[10%] text-blue-600 text-4xl font-bold z-20 animate-pulse">+</div>
  </div>

  <img 
    src="/images/component2.png" 
    alt="" 
    class="absolute bottom-[15%] lg:bottom-[6%] left-[80%] lg:left-[45%] -translate-y-1/2 w-[6%] lg:w-[3%] z-0 opacity-90"
  />

  <img 
    src="/images/ellipse bajo.png" 
    alt="" 
    class="absolute bottom-[-5%] lg:bottom-[-10%] left-0 w-[120%] lg:w-[110%] max-w-none lg:max-w-[600px] z-0 opacity-80"
  />
</section>